                  <rs id="t18730113-104-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18730113-104-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18730113-104-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>, for a like offence.</rs>
